{"tid":765454,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【屎朗，不了】希古恩抵米蘭 將以1800萬歐元借A米","createTime":"2018-08-02T18:11:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-03T00:44:22.000Z","uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"670e16a7a2a173ffa01597a6a0a6038c235767a1","tid":765454,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T18:11:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgsa.baidu.com/forum/w%3D580/sign=76ec74a6593d26972ed3085565fbb24f/3c2e48fbfbedab64d54f04acff36afc379311eba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgsa.baidu.com%2Fforum%2Fw%253D580%2Fsign%3D76ec74a6593d26972ed3085565fbb24f%2F3c2e48fbfbedab64d54f04acff36afc379311eba.jpg&h=1fc493db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n隨著C朗強勢加盟，祖雲達斯決定為鋒線「減磅」把前鋒希古恩外借AC米蘭，這位阿根廷射手已抵達米蘭準備接受體測，據報借用一季費用高達1,800萬歐元。<br />\n<br />\n為祖記上陣105場射入55球的希古恩，共為球隊贏得兩季聯賽及意盃雙料冠軍，但C朗高價加盟除影響其地位外，亦令祖記必須「開源節流」，以1,800萬歐元把他外借AC米蘭一季，完成後後者可以3,600萬歐元的轉會費作永久收購。<br />\n<br />\n雖然AC米蘭教練加度素不欲多談轉會情況，但希古恩已抵達米蘭，他對記者說︰「我感覺很好，明天將進行體測，但願一切順利簽下新合約。我希望對AC米蘭的球迷表示尊敬，對祖雲達斯球迷亦一樣，因為他們一直支持我。」<br />\n<br />\n此外，只要加度素覓得中堅替補人選，轉會A米一季的守將邦路斯亦將以交換球員形式回歸祖記，而前者可換來中堅簡達拿加盟。(<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=jpmgNOnCDCzbp9Y%2BEr7Off%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=f6a61875\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img1.dongqiudi.com/fastdfs3/M00/3C/9A/ChOxM1tjK5-Ae9HEAAIPoC6bHZ0720.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg1.dongqiudi.com%2Ffastdfs3%2FM00%2F3C%2F9A%2FChOxM1tjK5-Ae9HEAAIPoC6bHZ0720.jpg&h=4d029a0e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"795a9877b10af4c121b6298cafa15ec5c8699845","tid":765454,"uid":70754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T18:22:29.000Z","msg":"題外話 A米俾PUMA做好唔慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6df8bbec0ea9bb6d5dcfbcb5b3138ffb1ec1609","tid":765454,"uid":627